00:38:14,835 --> 00:38:18,351
Moreover, the families left behind
will come over to help too.

549
00:38:19,016 --> 00:38:22,351
So you don't have to worry about
her living and safety.

550
00:38:23,176 --> 00:38:24,056
I know.

551
00:38:25,591 --> 00:38:26,471
Why?

552
00:38:27,062 --> 00:38:28,062
Any other concerns?

553
00:38:31,616 --> 00:38:32,496
Brigade Commander,

554
00:38:34,480 --> 00:38:36,200
can you inform Tian Yong
to return and see Xue?

555
00:38:38,031 --> 00:38:38,951
What do you say?

556
00:38:39,942 --> 00:38:42,911
I have no idea where Tian Yong is.

557
00:38:43,328 --> 00:38:44,406
Right now,

558
00:38:44,447 --> 00:38:46,047
this isn't what we should worry about.

559
00:38:46,581 --> 00:38:48,080
After redeployment,

560
00:38:48,121 --> 00:38:49,855
joint military exercise
will be conducted right away.

561
00:38:50,391 --> 00:38:51,271
By then,

562
00:38:52,024 --> 00:38:53,491
the representatives of
the foreign militaries...

563
00:38:53,711 --> 00:38:55,840
have to attend it
except the captain of the war zone.

564
00:38:55,881 --> 00:38:56,881
Be well-prepared...

565
00:38:59,022 --> 00:39:00,062
and do your best.

566
00:39:00,311 --> 00:39:01,191
Yes.

567
00:39:03,741 --> 00:39:04,711
As soldiers,

568
00:39:05,200 --> 00:39:08,271
we can't choose the region
and era we're in.

569
00:39:08,720 --> 00:39:09,800
The only thing we can choose

570
00:39:11,816 --> 00:39:13,520
is loyalty to our era.

571
00:39:28,103 --> 00:39:33,840
♪I'd like to find out♪

572
00:39:34,703 --> 00:39:39,520
♪If my mask of foolishness♪

573
00:39:41,000 --> 00:39:46,480
♪Could deceive you♪

574
00:39:47,240 --> 00:39:51,480
♪I'm putting on my best performance♪

575
00:39:53,407 --> 00:39:59,160
♪Is it a little too cruel?♪

576
00:39:59,744 --> 00:40:04,480
♪The game of adults♪

577
00:40:06,200 --> 00:40:11,941
♪The moments of joy along the way♪

578
00:40:12,438 --> 00:40:17,868
♪Do not bring them up♪

579
00:40:18,880 --> 00:40:24,751
♪Whatever evidence♪

580
00:40:25,320 --> 00:40:30,471
♪Requires no validation♪

581
00:40:31,728 --> 00:40:37,591
♪It is our shared secret♪

582
00:40:38,058 --> 00:40:44,118
♪Keeping it close to the heart♪

583
00:40:44,183 --> 00:40:50,000
♪The embrace I long for♪

584
00:40:50,615 --> 00:40:55,520
♪Comes up in my dreams often♪

585
00:40:56,937 --> 00:41:02,800
♪If I hang in there♪

586
00:41:03,336 --> 00:41:10,336
♪I know love will surely come, someday♪

587
00:41:20,595 --> 00:41:21,890
The operation went well.

588
00:41:22,150 --> 00:41:23,150
You've worked hard.

589
00:41:23,431 --> 00:41:24,551
Thank you, Chief Chen.

590
00:41:28,461 --> 00:41:33,877
♪The game of adults♪

591
00:41:34,980 --> 00:41:40,881
♪The moments of joy along the way♪

592
00:41:41,218 --> 00:41:45,519
♪Do not bring them up♪

593
00:41:45,560 --> 00:41:47,101
Keep both sides symmetric
when inserting the needles.

594
00:41:47,813 --> 00:41:49,160
Don't leave dead spaces subcutaneously.

595
00:41:51,709 --> 00:41:52,760
Why are you being so nervous?

596
00:41:54,484 --> 00:41:55,520
Try to think...

597
00:41:57,031 --> 00:41:58,880
how you usually stitch
the grape skins up.

598
00:42:00,240 --> 00:42:05,971
♪It is our shared secret♪

599
00:42:06,526 --> 00:42:12,160
♪Keeping it close to the heart♪

600
00:42:12,766 --> 00:42:18,760
♪The embrace I long for♪

601
00:42:19,018 --> 00:42:24,640
♪Comes up in my dreams often♪

602
00:42:25,396 --> 00:42:31,200
♪If I hang in there♪

603
00:42:42,368 --> 00:42:43,648
Xia Chu, here's your parcel.

604
00:42:44,470 --> 00:42:45,350
Thank you.

605
00:43:19,933 --> 00:43:21,293
I'll protect you for Mu Ze.

606
00:43:47,920 --> 00:43:49,000
I received the figure.

607
00:43:56,560 --> 00:43:57,440
Is it handsome?

608
00:44:00,735 --> 00:44:01,985
Not as handsome as you.

609
00:44:06,808 --> 00:44:07,798
Of course.

610
00:44:25,032 --> 00:44:26,280
How's the new outpost?

611
00:44:49,866 --> 00:44:51,346
Boss, are you there?

612
00:44:52,023 --> 00:44:53,543
I want to customize a figure.

613
00:45:44,473 --> 00:45:45,353
Goodbye, fellow students.

614
00:45:45,791 --> 00:45:48,311
Goodbye, teacher!

615
00:45:54,120 --> 00:45:55,000
Xia Chu?

616
00:45:55,519 --> 00:45:56,399
You're here.

617
00:45:58,471 --> 00:45:59,351
Where is Xiao Xiao?

618
00:46:00,552 --> 00:46:02,272
Two patients came to
the emergency department abruptly.

619
00:46:02,313 --> 00:46:03,993
I think she couldn't
get away at the moment.

620
00:46:04,034 --> 00:46:05,194
So I come here by myself.

621
00:46:08,806 --> 00:46:10,446
This is the honey from her.

622
00:46:10,614 --> 00:46:13,141
Her father
bought this from the beekeeper.

623
00:46:13,182 --> 00:46:14,062
It's all-natural.

624
00:46:14,942 --> 00:46:15,783
That's great.

625
00:46:15,824 --> 00:46:16,744
Thank her for me.

626
00:46:19,231 --> 00:46:20,720
These are our thesis.

627
00:46:20,761 --> 00:46:21,891
We had amended two drafts.

628
00:46:22,168 --> 00:46:23,800
Okay.
Let me read them.

629
00:46:26,131 --> 00:46:29,351
Are you still in touch with Ms. Meng Zhen?

630
00:46:31,326 --> 00:46:32,526
I've been busy lately.

631
00:46:33,329 --> 00:46:35,329
I have many works in school.

632
00:46:36,544 --> 00:46:37,664
A little while ago,

633
00:46:38,104 --> 00:46:40,000
she took Xiao Jun to our
hospital for medical checkup...

634
00:46:41,205 --> 00:46:42,885
and said she's going to Beijing.

635
00:46:43,664 --> 00:46:44,544
Really?

636
00:46:46,231 --> 00:46:47,111
By the way,

637
00:46:47,756 --> 00:46:48,636
how is it?

638
00:46:48,809 --> 00:46:49,879
How does it feel to be back...

639
00:46:51,323 --> 00:46:52,280
at the Cardiac Surgery Department?

640
00:46:54,094 --> 00:46:58,231
I'm not used to stitch the patient up
during operation at first.

641
00:46:59,520 --> 00:47:00,400
Never mind.

642
00:47:00,590 --> 00:47:01,630
You'll get used to it.

643
00:47:02,031 --> 00:47:02,911
You're like me.

644
00:47:03,751 --> 00:47:05,120
I'm currently adapting to the life...

645
00:47:05,695 --> 00:47:07,280
which I don't have to stitch patients up.

646
00:47:08,390 --> 00:47:09,270
Everything will be fine.

647
00:47:15,255 --> 00:47:16,922
I'm preparing to sign up
for the military exercise.

648
00:47:19,160 --> 00:47:20,040
Is Liang Mu Ze going?

649
00:47:20,873 --> 00:47:21,753
I don't know.

650
00:47:22,616 --> 00:47:23,880
I think he'll go.

651
00:47:24,431 --> 00:47:25,311
I can feel it.

652
00:47:26,048 --> 00:47:26,928
Sir,

653
00:47:27,495 --> 00:47:28,375
thank you.

654
00:47:29,197 --> 00:47:31,160
About me returning to
the Cardiac Surgery Department,

655
00:47:31,201 --> 00:47:34,525
things wouldn't be this smooth
if you hadn't talked to the chief.

656
00:47:34,760 --> 00:47:35,640
Don't say that.

657
00:47:36,865 --> 00:47:37,745
I think...

658
00:47:38,471 --> 00:47:40,200
you deserve this.

659
00:47:41,101 --> 00:47:41,981
It's true.

660
00:47:46,088 --> 00:47:49,311
If you really want to thank me,
how about this?

661
00:47:50,671 --> 00:47:51,551
Clean the blackboard.

662
00:47:52,993 --> 00:47:53,873
No problem.

663
00:48:20,920 --> 00:48:21,840
Sir,

664
00:48:23,057 --> 00:48:24,017
I'll keep that in mind.
